summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Twenty-six and 67/100 Dollars ($26.67), or so much thereof as may be necessary from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 1904 and 1909 general taxes against the east eight (8) feet of Lot One (1) to six (6) inclusive, Block Twenty-two (22), Ede's and Knights Addition.
